{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Cartridge - Create track from Media Explorer\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Creates a new track with Cartridge sampler and loads the selected file from Media Explorer. If nothing is selected, opens a file dialog.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Requirements:}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Cartridge 0.3.1+\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab js_ReaScriptAPI extension\sa180\par}
}

