{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Cartridge - Load sample to active instance\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Loads the selected file from Media Explorer into the currently focused Cartridge instance. Similar to ReaSamplOmatic's "Reuse Active Sample player" action.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Usage:}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Open Cartridge on any track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Select a file in Media Explorer\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Run this script\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Requirements:}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Cartridge 0.3.1+\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab js_ReaScriptAPI extension\sa180\par}
}

